					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12829549#post-4431774</guid>
				<title>Mabuhay!</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12829549/scp-3906#post-4431774</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2019 03:55:27 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>PeppersGhost</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1553042</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is a rewrite of the previous SCP-3906 that I wrote for JamCon '18. Given the 24 hour time constraint, I wasn't able to take the article quite as far as I wanted to. It's a piece that's really close to my heart, though, and I felt it was deserving of a more fleshed-out treatment. To see the original and its comment thread, please look under 'Files' at the bottom of the article.</p> <p>Numen is a <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/esoteric-classes-complete-list">subclass</a> that refers to deific anomalies.</p> <p>Special thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mortos" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1705184&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1575764398" alt="Mortos" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1705184)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mortos" >Mortos</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cadavercommander" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3187823&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1575764398" alt="CadaverCommander" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3187823)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cadavercommander" >CadaverCommander</a></span> for some very helpful feedback on this.</p> <p>If <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-2190">SCP-2190</a> didn't make my roots obvious, this one certainly does!</p> <p>Source photos: <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/m_kajo/24434626189/">1</a> <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/shankaronline/9103467843">2</a> <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Balut001.jpg">3</a>.</p> <hr /> <div style="text-align: center;"> <p>Discover more of my weird ramblings in<br /> <span style="font-size:125%;"><strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/dr-john-peppersghost-pepper-s-personnel-file">~PeppersGhost's Gallery of Illusion!~</a></strong></span></p> </div> <hr /> 
				 	]]>
